<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="powerful-adj">powerful <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'paʊəfl/    美 /'paʊərfl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>强壮的；强健的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a powerful body
强健的体魄</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>强大的；有权势的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a powerful arm 
强健的胳膊</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Never before has our country been so powerful as it is today. 
我们的祖国从来没有像现在这样强大。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>作用大的；效力大的</strong></h4>
<p>having a strong effect：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a powerful drug
疗效显著的药</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Good teamwork is a <strong>powerful tool</strong> (= very effective method) for effective management.
良好的团队是有效管理的利器。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>powerfully  /'paʊəfəli/ adv   </p></div>